{"dialogue":[
  [{"role":"user","content":"What is a fraction?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"If you cut a pizza into 4 equal pieces and take 1, what do you call that piece in fraction form?"}],
  [{"role":"user","content":"That would be 1/4."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Great. What do the top and bottom numbers tell us in a fraction like 1/4?"}],
  [{"role":"user","content":"The top number tells how many slices there are in the whole pizza. (false)"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Close idea. The bottom shows into how many equal parts the whole is divided. If the pizza is cut into 4 equal parts, what fraction is one piece?"}]
] }

